  <entry>
    <title>HTML 常用标签</title>
    <url>/2023/05/02/HTML%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E6%A0%87%E7%AD%BE/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><script class="meting-secondary-script-marker" src="\assets\js\Meting.min.js"></script><h2>HTML 标题</h2>
<font size=3>标题是通过 h1-h6 标签进行定义的，标题一共有 6 个，如 h1 表示一级标题，h2 表示二级标题，以此类推一直到六级标题，语法如下：
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">h1</span>&gt;</span>标题内容<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">h1</span>/&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">hr</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
其中还可以通过 hr 标签给标题下面画一条分割线(就是一条加粗的直线)。
</font>
<h2>HTML 段落</h2>
<font size=3>
在 html 中通过 p 标签来表示一个段落，可以通过该标签在 html 文档中生成若干个段落，段落中可以通过 <br> 标签进行换行，语法如下：
</font>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">p</span>&gt;</span>段落内容<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">p</span>/&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2>HTML 文本格式化</h2>
<font size=3>常用的几个文本格式化：</font>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">b</span>&gt;</span>加粗文本 <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">b</span>&gt;</span> <span class="comment">&lt;!-- 通常用 &lt;strong&gt; 标签替换 &lt;b&gt; 使用 --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">i</span>&gt;</span> 斜体文本 <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">i</span>&gt;</span> <span class="comment">&lt;!-- 通常用 &lt;em&gt; 替换 &lt;i&gt; 使用 --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">code</span>&gt;</span> 定义计算机代码 <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">code</span>&gt;</span> <span class="comment">&lt;!-- 该标签用于表示计算机源代码或者其他机器可以阅读的文本内容 --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">sub</span>&gt;</span> 下标 <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">sub</span>&gt;</span>  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">sup</span>&gt;</span> 上标 <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">sup</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">small</span>&gt;</span> 定义小号文本 <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">small</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">del</span>&gt;</span> 定义删除字 <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">del</span>&gt;</span><span class="comment">&lt;!-- 在文本的中间插过一条直线 --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">ins</span>&gt;</span> 定义插入字<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">ins</span>&gt;</span><span class="comment">&lt;!-- 在文本下面多出一条下划线 --&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2>HTML 链接</h2>
<font size=3>
在 html 中用 a 标签来定义一个链接，链接简单理解就是一个网址，通过点击该标签框住的文字可以跳转到相应的网页网站等，这里通过 a 标签内的一个 herf 属性来表示即将要跳转的链接地址, 语法如下：
</font>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">a</span> <span class="attr">herf</span>=<span class="string">&#x27;url&#x27;</span>&gt;</span>链接文本 <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">a</span>&gt;</span> </span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">a</span> <span class="attr">herf</span>=<span class="string">&#x27;https://www.baidu.com&#x27;</span>&gt;</span> 跳转到百度<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">a</span>&gt;</span><span class="comment">&lt;!-- 实例 --&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<font size=3>当然如果暂时不想跳转可以定义 herf 属性值为“#”，如:</font>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">a</span> <span class="attr">herf</span>=<span class="string">&quot;#&quot;</span>&gt;</span>表示一个空链接<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">a</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<font size=3>
锚点链接：目标位置添加一个 id href="#(id 名字)"，作用跳转到该 id 元素所在的位置。标签 a 链接中的 target 属性表示可以使用该属性定义链接的文档 (网站网页等) 在何处显示，就是通过哪种方式打开的意思。target 的属性值有 _self,_blank,_parent,_top。_self 表示默认跳转方式，在原来的窗口打开(在同一框架或窗口中打开所链接的文档)，_blank 表示
在新浏览器窗口中打开链接文件，_parent 将链接的文件载入含有该链接框架的父框架集或父窗口中。_top 在当前的整个浏览器窗口中打开所链接的文档，因而会删除所有框架。
</font>
<h2>HTML 图像</h2>
<font size=3>在 html 中用 img 标签来定义插入一张图片，语法如下：</font>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">img</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">&#x27;url&#x27;</span> <span class="attr">art</span>=<span class="string">&#x27;some_text&#x27;</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<font size=3>
img 这里有两个属性，一个 src 表示图像的链接地址，art 表示当图片无法显示时，用该属性值 (描述该图片的文本) 来表示该图片。其中还可以设置属性 width(表示宽)，height(表示高)，可以用来设置该图片的大小。
</font>

<h2>HTML 表格</h2>
<font size=3>
在 html 中用 table 标签来定义一个表格，table 标签中有若干行用 tr 标签来表示，每一行分成若干份表示每个单元格，用 td 标签来表示。表格还可以更规范一些，用 thead 标签表示表格的表头，表头中标题用 th 标签表示，tboody 标签表示表格的内容主体，tfoot 表示表格的页眉。实例如下：
</font>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">table</span> <span class="attr">border</span>=<span class="string">&quot;1&quot;</span> <span class="attr">align</span>=<span class="string">&quot;center&quot;</span> <span class="attr">cellpadding</span>=<span class="string">&quot;10&quot;</span> <span class="attr">cellspacing</span>=<span class="string">&quot;0&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">&lt;!-- </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">cellpadding 像素值，规定单元边缘格与内容之间的空白，默认 1 像素，cellspacing 像素值，</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">规定单元格之间的空白，默认为 2 像素 </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">--&gt;</span>        </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">thead</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">&lt;!-- thead 用于定义表格的头部 --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">tr</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">th</span>&gt;</span>排名 <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">th</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">th</span>&gt;</span> 关键词 <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">th</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">th</span>&gt;</span> 今日搜索 <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">th</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">th</span>&gt;</span> 最近七日 <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">th</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">tr</span>&gt;</span>    </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">thead</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">&lt;!-- tbody 用于定义表格主体，主要用于放数据本体  --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">tbody</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">tr</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span> 鬼吹灯 <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span>345<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span>67955<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span> 贴吧，图片，百科 <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">tr</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">tr</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span> 鬼吹灯 <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span>345<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span>67955<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span> 贴吧，图片，百科 <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">tr</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">tr</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span> 鬼吹灯 <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span>345<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span>67955<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span> 贴吧，图片，百科<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">tr</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">tbody</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">table</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<font size=3>td 中的属性 rowspan=“合并单元格行数” 跨行合并 colspan=“合并单元格列数” 跨列合并。合并之后还需要减去 (删除) 合并的单元格。
<h2>HTML 列表</h2>
html 中有 ul 无序列表，ol 有序列表，dl 自定义列表。无序列表用 ul 标签表示，列表内用 li 标签表示列表的每一项，语法如下：
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">ul</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span>第一项 <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span> 第二项 <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span> 第三项 <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span> 第四项<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">ul</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
有序列表 用 ol 标签表示，列表内也是用 li 来表示列表中的每一项，语法如下：
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">ol</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span>第一项 <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span> 第二项 <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span> 第三项 <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span> 第四项<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">ol</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
自定义列表 用 dl 标签表示，列表中用 dt 标签来表示每一项的项目(名字)，dd 标签描述每一个项目(名字)，标签 dt 与 dd 属于兄弟标签，语法如下：
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">dl</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">dt</span>&gt;</span>项目名 1<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">dt</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">dd</span>&gt;</span>项目名 1 描述 <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">dd</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">dd</span>&gt;</span> 项目名 1 描述 <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">dd</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">dt</span>&gt;</span> 项目名 2<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">dt</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">dd</span>&gt;</span>项目名 2 描述 <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">dd</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">dd</span>&gt;</span> 项目名 2 描述<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">dd</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">dl</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2>HTML 表单</h2>
html 表单用于收集用户的输入信息。用 form 来定义一个表单，在 HTML 中一个完整的表单通常是由表单域，表单控件（也称表单元素）和提示信息 3 个部分组成。
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">form</span> <span class="attr">action</span>=<span class="string">&quot;url 地址 &quot;</span> <span class="attr">method</span>=<span class="string">&quot; 提交方式 &quot;</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">&quot; 表单域名称 &quot;</span> &gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    各种表单元素控件</span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">form</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
下面是一个常用的表单实例，里面包含常用的表单元素：
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">form</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">&lt;!-- 文本框 用户可以在里面输入任何文字 maxlength 表示最大输入长度,minlength 表示最小输入长度 --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    用户名：<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">input</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">&quot;text&quot;</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">&quot;username&quot;</span> <span class="attr">value</span>=<span class="string">&quot; 表示值，写入的内容 &quot;</span> <span class="attr">placeholder</span>=<span class="string">&quot; 请输入用户名（提示信息）&quot;</span> <span class="attr">maxlength</span>=<span class="string">&quot;6&quot;</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">br</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">&lt;!-- 密码框， --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    密码：<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">input</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">&quot;password&quot;</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">br</span>&gt;</span><span class="comment">&lt;!-- type 类型 --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">&lt;!-- 单选按钮 可以实现多选一 --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    性别：男 <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">input</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">&quot;radio&quot;</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">&quot;xibie&quot;</span>&gt;</span> 女 <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">input</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">&quot;radio&quot;</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">&quot;xibie&quot;</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">br</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">&lt;!-- 多选框 可以实现多选 --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    爱好：吃饭 <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">input</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">&quot;checkbox&quot;</span> <span class="attr">checked</span>=<span class="string">&quot;checked&quot;</span>&gt;</span> 睡觉 <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">input</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">&quot;checkbox&quot;</span>&gt;</span> 打豆豆 <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">input</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">&quot;checkbox&quot;</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">br</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">input</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">&quot;submit&quot;</span> <span class="attr">value</span>=<span class="string">&quot; 注册 &quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">input</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">&quot;reset&quot;</span> <span class="attr">value</span>=<span class="string">&quot; 重置 &quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">input</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">&quot;button&quot;</span> <span class="attr">value</span>=<span class="string">&quot; 按钮 &quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    文件上传 <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">input</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">&quot;file&quot;</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span> <span class="attr">id</span>=<span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">label</span> <span class="attr">for</span>=<span class="string">&quot;te&quot;</span>&gt;</span> 用户名 <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">label</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">input</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">&quot;text&quot;</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span> <span class="attr">id</span>=<span class="string">&quot;te&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    籍贯：<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">select</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span> <span class="attr">id</span>=<span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span>&gt;</span>  <span class="comment">&lt;!-- 下拉选项列表 --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">             <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">option</span> <span class="attr">value</span>=<span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span>&gt;</span> 山东 <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">option</span>&gt;</span>  <span class="comment">&lt;!-- 下拉选项列表中的具体每一项内容 --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">             <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">option</span> <span class="attr">value</span>=<span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span>&gt;</span> 北京 <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">option</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">             <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">option</span> <span class="attr">value</span>=<span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span> <span class="attr">selected</span>=<span class="string">&quot;selected&quot;</span>&gt;</span> 火星<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">option</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">          <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">select</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    今日反馈：</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">textarea</span> <span class="attr">cols</span>=<span class="string">&quot;50&quot;</span> <span class="attr">rows</span>=<span class="string">&quot;6&quot;</span>&gt;</span> <span class="comment">&lt;!-- 多行文本框输入  cols 表示多少行，rows 表示多少列 --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">textarea</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">form</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2>HTML 区块</h2>
HTML 中用 div 与 span 来把元素组合起来，大多数 HTML 元素被定义为块级元素或内联元素。<br>
块级元素在浏览器显示时，通常会以新行来开始（和结束）实例：h1,p,ul,table<br>
内联元素在浏览器显示时，通常不会以新行开始，实例：b,td,a,img<br>
HTML 中 div 标签是块级元素，它可以用于组合其他 HTML 元素，是一个容器，方便用于文档布局，设置样式等，默认独占一行。<br>
span 标签是内联元素，它可以用作为文本的容器，没有特殊含义，与 css 一起使用时可以为部分文本设置样式属性，默认为内容多大就站多大。
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span>块元素 <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">span</span>&gt;</span> 行内元素<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">span</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</font>
